>号）、五官科医院（南城河路<span>12</span>号）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">招标内容：主院区骨三、普三病区入口墙面护墙板铺贴，<span>1</span>号手术室顶面裂缝注浆处理、设备层漏水处理，检验科微生物室制作隔断；北区新做医疗废物转运车，<span>9</span>号楼屋面漏水维修，高压氧舱屋面伸缩缝漏水维修等项目。具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">发包方式：包工包料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标人资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">投标人须具有有效的建筑装修装饰工程专业承包二级及以上施工资质的独立法人，并具有有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">截止<span>2021</span>年<span>10</span>月在盐城市第一人民医院存在已中标工程项目，且投标人未按合同工期完成并通过招标人验收的，一年内不得报名参与本单位招标项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>10</span>月<span>28</span>日<span>8</span>时至<span>2021</span>年<span>11</span>月<span>2</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">、本项目评标办法采用“合理低价法”。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"fon