deograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt;\r\nline-height:44.8pt;background:white\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312;color:#222222;background:white\"><a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/11/12/20211112140123059.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<img src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/11/12/20211112140123059_s.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a><br>\r\n</span></p>','','','','','');
