ph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目地点：盐城市毓龙西路</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">166</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">号。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目规模：盐城市老年康复医院建设主要分为改造工程与新建工程，改建工程与新建工程分开立项。改造工程包含对市一院北区门诊楼、急诊楼、</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">号病房楼、</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">号病房等进行改造及周边环境整治，改造总建筑面积</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">5.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万平方米，预算约</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.28</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">亿元。新建停车综合楼，建筑面积</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">4.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，主要解决医院停车难及随着现代医学发展导致的医院功能用房不足。新建停车综合楼，设计地下</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">层，地上</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">15</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">层，地下</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，地上</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">3.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，其中车库面积</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">万㎡，设置</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">600</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">个停车位，新建投资约</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\">2.36</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">亿元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、招标范围：盐城市老年康复医院改造和新建工程节能评估报告编制服务，投标人须与招标人充分沟通，了解项目的地点、投资额、所处环境、性质等各类可能影响报价的情况，将节能评估报告编制所需的人工费、材料费、评审费、交通差旅费、公众调查费、管理费、利润、规费、税金等综合考虑，总价包干，对编制材料的格式、深度等具体要求，以相关主管部门要求为准，确保通过相关部门的审核。招标人保留对上述暂定招标内容适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、服务期要求：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;color:black\"> 15 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">日历天内完成节能评估报告编制，具体服务时间以招标人通知为准。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、质量要求：满足国家及行业相关法律法规、标准规范要求，并确保通过招标人及相关行业主管部门技术的审核，并获得相应的批复。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">二、投标人须具备以下条件：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、投标人资格要求：投标人须是在中国境内注册，具有能力完成本次招标内容的独立法人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:black\">、项目负责人为投标人本单位正式职工，须具有相关专业中级及以上职称证书。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:\r\nchar;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric\"><span style=\"fon