\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>ICU</span>、<span>CCU</span>氧气管道改造工程。具体内容详见招标人提供的图纸及工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">工期要求：<span> 30 </span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的书面通知为准；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">发包方式：包工包料。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量要求：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有建设行政主管部门核发的机电安装工程施工总承包三级及以上资质或建筑机电安装工程专业承包三级及以上资质的独立法人，并取得安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人项目负责人必须是投标人本单位的正式职工，并具有机电安装工程专业的二级（含）以上建造师注册证书，同时具有安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有医疗器械生产许可证、医疗器械生产产品登记表。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有医用中心供氧系统《医疗器械注册证》以及《医疗器械注册登记表》。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、投标人应具有特种设备生产许可证<span> (</span>压力管道安装<span>)GC2</span>级。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.7</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.8</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、财务要求：投标人应具有独立订立合同的能力，未处于财产被接管、冻结和破产状态。\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.9</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、</span><b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">本项目评标办法采用“合理低价法”。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2323','3146','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院主院区2#直线加速器机房防辐射工程项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。1、工程概况 1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区2#直线加速器机房防辐射工程项目。1.2服务地点：盐城市第一人民','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1638348280','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>2#</span>直线加速器机房防辐射工程项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、工程概况<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>2#</span>直线加速器机房防辐射工程项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">服务地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">招标内容：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>2#</span>直线加速器机房防辐射工程，具体详见招标人提供的工程量清单和维保要求。</span><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标人保留调整此次招标规模的权力，具体根据招标人的要求按实结算，中标单价不变。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量标准：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">必须达到国家关于《放射性同位素与射线装置安全和防护条例》、《电离辐射防护与辐射源安全基本标准》、《医用<span>X</span>射线诊断卫生防护标准》、《医用<span>X</span>射线诊断卫生防护监测规范》《医用电子加速器卫防护标准》《临床核医学放射卫生防护标准》等的辐射防护法律法规的要求。并保证通过卫生、环保部门预评价、防护检测及竣工验收等环节。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2 </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">具有承担民事责任能力的独立法人企业。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">业绩要求：自<span>2018</span>年<span>1</span>月<span>1</span>日以来（以合同签订日期为准），投标人承担过类似辐射防护工程施工业绩。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3&nbsp; </span><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">本次招标不接受联合体投标。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">其他要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人须确保主要设备、材料（防辐射材料、防辐射门窗等）应具有卫生行政主管部门颁发的有效的《放射防护器材检测报告》；<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.4.2 </span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">信誉要求：投标人没有被国家、江苏省省级有关部门及盐城市级有关部门暂停招投标或市场准入资格且在公示处罚期内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、</span><b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">本项目采用“资格后审”，“综合评估法”</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2324','3147','1','','','盐城市第一人民医院主院区2#直线加速器机房装修工程项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。1、工程概况1.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区2#直线加速器机房装修工程项目。1.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1638348306','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>2#</span>直线加速器机房装修工程项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:24.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、工程概况</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>2#</span>直线加速器机房装修工程项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">招标内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区<span>2#</span>直线加速器机房装修工程。具体内容详见招标人提供的图纸及工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">工期要求：<span> 30 </span>日历天，具体开工日期以招标人的书面通知为准；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">发包方式：包工包料。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1.6</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">质量要求：</span><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">符合国家“合格”标准，质保期<span>2</span>年。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.1pt;line-height:24.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2、</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人应当具备的主要资格条件：</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:27.1pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">投标人须具备建设行政主管部门核发的建筑装修装饰工程专业承包二级及以上资质（或有效期内的建筑装修装饰工程总承包三级及以上）的独立法人企业，并取得有效的安全生产许可证。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:27.1pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">拟派的项目负责人须具有建筑工程二级及以上建造师执业资格，并具有安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:27.1pt;\r\nline-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;background:white\">投标人须保证项目</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">负责人</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">为本单位的正式职工，并确保从投标截止之日当月向前连续<span>6</span>个月均连续在本单位缴纳养老保险（例：如开标日期为<span>2021</span>年<span>7</span>月的某一天，则投标单位需保证以上人员<span>2021</span>年<span>1-6</span>月养老保险均在本单位缴纳）。（提供社保证明复印件）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:11.95pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:12.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">项目负责人从本工程投标文件递交截止之日起必须满足下列条件：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:11.95pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:12.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">（<span>1</span>）项目负责人不得同时在两个或者两个以上单位受聘或者执业。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:11.95pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:12.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">（<span>2</span>）项目负责人是非变更后无在建工程，或项目负责人是变更后无在建工程（必须原合同工期已满且变更备案之日已满<span>6</span>个月），或因非承包方原因致使工程项目停工或因故不能按期开工、且已办理了项目负责人解锁手续，或项目负责人有在建工程，但该在建工程与本次招标的工程属于同一工程项目、同一项目批文、同一施工地点分段发包或分期施工的情况且总的工程规模在项目负责人执业范围之内。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:11.95pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:12.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">（<span>3</span>）项目负责人无行贿犯罪行为记录；或者有行贿犯罪行为记录，但自记录之日起已超过<span>5</span>年的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:11.95pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:12.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">项目经理无在建工程指项目经理不得同时在其他建设工程项目中担任关键岗位人员、不在本项目兼任本项目的其它岗位。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-left:11.95pt;text-align:left;\r\ntext-indent:12.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体\">在建工程处于中标结果公告（直接发包的项目以网上合同备案为准）到合同约定的工程全部完成且竣工验收合格期间的工程。竣工验收证明是指由建设单位（或监理）组织工程建设各方验收合格，并签署相应的单位工程质量竣工验收记录或者分部工程质量验收记录等验收文件。（投标时提供无在建工程承诺书，格式自拟）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.1pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名并领取招标文件，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、</span><b><span style=\"font-family:\r\n宋体\">本项目评标办法采用“合理低价法”。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:24.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>1</span>日<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>','','','','','');
