t-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:black;background:white\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span lang=\"EN-US\">0515-66696810</span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black\"></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:23.0pt;\r\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:\r\nwhite\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:\r\nwhite\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:black;background:white\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;background:\r\nwhite;word-break:break-all\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n宋体;color:black;background:white\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">时间：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2021</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp; </span></span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2332','3155','1','','','1、盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。2、项目概况与招标内容2.1项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目。2.2项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路66号）、','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1638841655','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目，资金已落实，招标人盐城市第一人民医院现对该项目进行公开招标，诚邀潜在的投标人参加投标。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、项目概况与招标内容</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目名称：盐城市第一人民医院化粪池清理等项目。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院主院区（人民南路<span>66</span>号）、北区（毓龙西路<span>166</span>号）、五官科医院（南城河路<span>12</span>号）、儿童医院（毓龙西路<span>34</span>号）</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">招标内容：四个院区化粪池、窨井及室外排水管道清理等。具体内容详见招标人提供的工程量清单。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">2.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">发包方式：包工包料。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标人资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">投标人具备独立法人资格，营业执照经营范围与本次招标内容相适应。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标报名及招标文件的获取</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">请符合上述资质条件的投标人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）投标报名，投标报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>8</span>时至<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>11</span>日<span>18</span>时。联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:21.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">、本项目评标办法采用“合理低价法”。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、投标申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝投标报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;\r\nbackground:white\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:\r\nwhite\">、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院纪检监察室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:21.0pt;\r\nbackground:white\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">其余内容详见招标文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">招标人：盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:right;background:white;word-break:break-all\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:black;background:white\">时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>7</span>日<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2333','3156','1','','/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/08/20211208135725930_s.jpg','11月16日盐城市第一人民医院召开党委理论学习中心组学习扩大会议，专题学习十九届六中全会精神。盐城市第一人民医院党委书记查文章领学《中国共产党第十九届中央委员会第六次全体会议公报》并提要求。查文章强调要深入学习宣传贯彻党的十九届六中全会精神和市委第八次代','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1637052846','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">月<span>16</span>日盐城市第一人民医院召开党委理论学习中心组学习扩大会议，专题学习十九届六中全会精神。盐城市第一人民医院党委书记查文章领学《中国共产党第十九届中央委员会第六次全体会议公报》并提要求。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">查文章强调要深入学习宣传贯彻党的十九届六中全会精神和市委第八次代表大会精神，这也是当前和今后一段时期的首要政治任务。要砥砺初心使命，笃定前行持续干，各级党组织要认真开展学习，坚持原原本本学，联系实际学，领导带头学，深刻领会全会精神的重大意义；要聚焦发展重点，发挥优势创新干，提升履职能力，切实将学习贯彻党的六中全会精神的学习热情转化为工作动力，忠诚履职，勇于担当，敬业奉献，要积极兑现承诺，只争朝夕加油干；要紧密结合实际，把党的百年奋斗重大成就和历史经验转化为更高水平建设区域医疗中心的强大动力。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">会议中市一院各党委委员作学习党的十九届六中全会精神心得体会汇报。参加此次会议的还有医院中层以上干部。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<br>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-align:left;text-indent:28.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;<a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/08/20211208135725930.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/image/2021/12/08/20211208135725930_s.jpg\" border=\"0\"></a><br>\r\n</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2334','3157','1','','','11月30日，盐城市第一人民医院召开党委理论学习中心组学习，专题学习中国共产党江苏省第十四次代表大会精神。医院全体党委班子成员参加学习。市一院党委书记查文章领学《争当表率 争做示范 走在前列奋力谱写“强富美高”新江苏现代化建设新篇章》报告。领学市委传达学习','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1638259200','<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">11</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">月<span>30</span>日，盐城市第一人民医院召开党委理论学习中心组学习，专题学习中国共产党江苏省第十四次代表大会精神。医院全体党委班子成员参加学习。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:21.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">市一院党委书记查文章领学《争当表率 争做示范 走在前列奋力谱写“强富美高”新江苏现代化建设新篇章》报告。领学市委传达学习党代会精神和省委书记吴政隆参加盐城代表团审议是的讲话精神《坚决扛起三大光荣使命\r\n勇当沿海高质量发展排头兵》。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">市一院党委书记查文章要求医院全体干部职工认真学习贯彻党的十九届六中全会精神、中国共产党江苏省第十四次代表大会精神、盐城市第八次党代会精神，要统一思想，提高政治站位，凝心聚力将大会精神变成蓝图、变成动力，号召全院上下团结一致，坚决响应中央、省市委的号召，全面贯彻党的精神，努力奋斗，开创医院发展新篇章。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';text-indent:28.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋,仿宋_GB2312\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','','','');
