;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">具有良好的商业信誉。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">近<span>3</span>年内在经营活动中无严重不良记录。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">5.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">按要求填写《盐城市第一人民医院设备咨询报名表》（见附件）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:30.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">报名截止时间：<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>27</span>日<span>24</span>：<span>00</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\'\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:#333333\">联系人：李老师<span>&nbsp; </span>联系方式：<span>0515-88508946&nbsp;\r\nQQ:651830413(</span>推荐<span>)</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\'Calibri\',\'sans-serif\';margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:11.0pt;font-family:\'Tahoma\',\'sans-serif\'\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"/ewebeditor/sysimage/icon16/doc.gif\"><a href=\"/ewebeditor/uploadfile/file/2021/12/20/20211220161212760.docx\" target=\"_bl