2.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">万元。</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">项目地点：盐城市第一人民医院</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext;\r\nbackground:white\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">项目内容：盐城市第一人民医院主院区方仓<span>CT</span>设备机预评价、控制效果评价和环评服务，包括但不限于：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">）卫生：放射诊疗设备预评价和控制效果评价（含批复）、办理放射诊疗许可证；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;background:white\">（<span>2</span>）环保：办理环评及防护检测、办理辐射安全许可证；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;background:white\">（<span>3</span>）对放射诊疗设备和场所（包括卫生和环保）进行质量控制检测和放射工作场所职业病危害因素检测；采购人保留对上述暂定项目内容适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;background:white\">二、申请人资格要求</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">申请人是具有独立法人资格的单位，营业执照须具有相关经营范围，能独立承担民事责任；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">申请人具备职业卫生（放射卫生）技术服务机构乙级及以上资质；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">申请人资质需经省级及以上卫生主管部门和环保主管部门认可；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">本项目</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">不接受</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">联合体。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext;background:white\">三、谈判报名及谈判文件的获取</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">谈判报名及谈判文件的获取，请符合上述资质条件的</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">申请</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">人携带单位介绍信（或授权委托书，须注明联系人、电话及邮箱）原件到江苏仁禾中衡工程咨询房地产估价有限公司造价二部（盐城市青年西路<span>8</span>号<span>8</span>楼<span>805</span>室）报名； </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">报名时间<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>28</span>日<span>8</span>时<span>30</span>分至<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>31</span>日<span>18</span>时；<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">联系人：刘永杰，<span>0515-69057406</span>；手机：<span>13626222271</span>；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;background:white\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;background:white\">售价：<span>300</span>元。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">四、响应文件提交</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">截止时间：<span>2022</span>年<span>1</span>月<span>5</span>日<span>15</span>时<span>00</span>分；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;\r\nfont-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">地点：盐城市第一人民医院南区门诊四楼会议室（盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">五、本项目采购方式：竞争性谈判。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">六、申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">七、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\", serif; color: black; text-align: right; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 26pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:right;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:\r\n宋体;color:windowtext\">盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: right; text-indent: 20.95pt; line-height: 17.55pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \"Times New Roman\", serif; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:windowtext\">2021</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:windowtext\">年<span>12</span>月<span>28</span>日</span></p>','','','','','');
INSERT INTO `p8_cms_item_article_addon` (`id`,`iid`,`page`,`addon_title`,`addon_frame`,`addon_summary`,`ip`,`last_update_ip`,`timestamp`,`content`,`custom_f`,`custom_g`,`custom_h`,`custom_i`,`custom_j`) VALUES ('2359','3182','1','','','一、盐城市儿童医院一期工程保健楼钢结构连廊项目已经相关部门批准建设。工程所需资金自筹，已落实。项目已具备招标条件，现对该本工程进行公开招标。本次招标对投标报名人的资格审查采用资格后审方法确定合格的投标人。 二、盐城市招标代理有限公司受招标人委托具体负','172.16.100.2','172.16.100.2','1640672280','<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">一、盐城市儿童医院一期工程保健楼钢结构连廊项目已经相关部门批准建设。工程所需资金自筹，已落实。项目已具备招标条件，现对该本工程进行公开招标。本次招标对投标报名人的资格审查采用资格后审方法确定合格的投标人。<span><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>二、</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\r\n宋体\">盐城市招标代理有限公司</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">受招标人委托具体负责本工程的招标事宜。<span><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>三、项目概况</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、项目名称：盐城市儿童医院一期工程保健楼钢结构连廊项目。<span>&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程地点：盐城市毓龙西路<span>6</span>号。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、工程规模：造价约<span>45</span>万元。 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体\">、质量标准<span>: </span>合格。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">5、</span><span style=\"color:black\">工期要求：<span>30</span>日历天。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">四、招标内容<span><br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>盐城市儿童医院一期工程保健楼钢结构连廊项目的施工<span style=\"color:black\">，具体数量及规格等要求详见工程量清单和设计图纸，招标人保留对上述工程规模进行适当调整的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">五、投标人主要资格要求<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"color:black\">1</span><span style=\"color:black\">、投标人资质要求：</span>投标人须具有建设行政主管部门核发的钢结构工程专业承包三级及以上施工资质的独立法人，并取得有效的安全生产许可证。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span>2</span>、项目负责人<span style=\"color:black\">的资格要求：项目负责人必须是投标人本单位的正式职工，并具有建筑工程专业的二级（含）以上建造师注册证书，同时应具有安全生产考核合格证（<span>B</span>类）。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">六、投标保证金：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">本项目投标保证金为人民币捌仟元整，具体交纳方式详见招标文件约定。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">七、本项目评标办法采用“<b>竞争性磋商</b>”。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">八、投标报名及招标文件领取时间和地点</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:25.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">请符合要求的潜在投标人于<span>2021</span>年<span>12</span>月<span>28</span>日至<span>2022</span>年<s